<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Candidate Account - Complete Your Profile</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .welcome-box {
      background-color: #f8f9ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .credential-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #f0f2ff 100%);
      border: 2px solid #667eea;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .credential-box .label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .credential-box .value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #667eea;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .credential-box .info-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .password-warning {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #856404;
    }

    .password-warning strong {
      color: #664d03;
    }

    .instructions {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .instructions h3 {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      color: #667eea;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .instructions ol {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .instructions li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #667eea;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ You've Been Nominated!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-box">
        <p style="margin:0; font-size: 16px;">
          <strong>Hi {{candidateName}},</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          You've been nominated as a candidate for <strong class="highlight">{{eventName}}</strong>! 
          A temporary account has been created for you to complete your candidate profile.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="password-warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This is a <strong>temporary account</strong>. You must log in and complete your profile for it to be published and visible to voters.
      </div>

      <p>
        To get started, use these credentials to log into your candidate portal:
      </p>

      <div class="credential-box">
        <div class="label">Email Address</div>
        <div class="value">{{email}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="credential-box">
        <div class="label">Temporary Password</div>
        <div class="value">{{temporaryPassword}}</div>
        <div class="info-text">
          ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Change this password immediately</strong> after your first login
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="instructions">
        <h3>üìã Next Steps</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Click the button below</strong> to access your candidate portal</li>
          <li><strong>Log in</strong> using the email and temporary password above</li>
          <li><strong>Change your password</strong> to something secure and memorable</li>
          <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> with all required information (bio, photos, etc.)</li>
          <li><strong>Submit for review</strong> - your profile will be reviewed by our team</li>
          <li><strong>Get approved</strong> - once approved, your profile goes live!</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Complete Your Candidate Profile</a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
        <strong>üí° What Happens Next?</strong>
      </p>
      <ul style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Your profile starts in <strong>Pending</strong> status until you complete it</li>
        <li>After you submit, it moves to <strong>Under Review</strong></li>
        <li>Once approved by our team, your profile becomes <strong>Published</strong></li>
        <li>Published profiles are visible to all voters in the event</li>
        <li>Any future updates to your profile will require re-approval</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="password-warning" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <strong>üîí Security Reminder:</strong> Never share your password with anyone. Our team will never ask for your password via email or phone.
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        If you have any questions or didn't expect this email, please contact our support team immediately.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from <strong>ITFY E-Voting Platform</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com">Contact Support</a> |
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}">Candidate Portal</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
        ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
